'''Furious Gaming''' is an Argentinian professional multi-gaming organization formed in March 2011. They announced their first ''League of Legends'' team in December 2013.

== History ==
On December 17, 2013, Furious Gaming's League team was created by picking up [[Lemondogs Argentina]].

